job.body:
Total vacancies:Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Telephone Operator

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by Advanced Centre For Treatment, Research, And Education In Cancer for the vacancies of Telephone Operator. If you are finding a government job in Mumbai then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Mumbai, from 20-05-2021, and till 23.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Mumbai and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for ACTREC Telephone Operator posts in Mumbai:

  • To apply for telephone Operator vacancies in Mumbai, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 20-05-2021
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 23.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40  years old.

ACTREC Telephone Operator Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 20,000-25,000 per month

How to apply for ACTREC Telephone Operator Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Mumbai. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of ACTREC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY ACTREC.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
